{"tid":1536920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母幾時先有麻包袋吖","createTime":"2019-09-03T18:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T18:04:00.000Z","uid":314825,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0a9bbd82272c928e802755fc2a8cce5bba3be0","tid":1536920,"uid":314825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:00:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">班狗而家係<span style=\"color: red;\">殺人</span>吖！屌你老母</span><br />\n我地打殘幾個唔過份吖<br />\n有幾多個手足已經比班狗比班黑社會打殘<br />\n30幾個新屋嶺<br />\n3個爆眼<br />\n1個小腿完全無知覺<br />\n1個打斷脊椎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有3個不知所蹤</span><br />\n<br />\n班狗呢？<br />\n咩懲罰都無<br />\n<br />\n就算係遲d 佢地受法律制裁<br />\n咪又係坐十碌廿碌<br />\n出到嚟咪又係四肢健全<br />\n<br />\n我地d 手足呢<br />\n唔單止受傷，可能會永久殘廢，仲要可能比人告<br />\n<br />\n法律制裁係咪真係仲有撚用？<br />\n<br />\n左膠，大愛撚請收皮，唔撚好話佢地都係人，佢地都係聽order 做野，佢地臨老會衰收尾，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我要現世報</span></span>,個天唔肯報我就人手幫佢報。<br />\n<br />\n佢地係人，咁我地d 手足呢，就唔撚係人吖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係香港法律制裁無撚用㗎啦</span>"},{"pid":"1f1e873d69fd3b7d83966f9634a00caa58e4da9a","tid":1536920,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:00:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.